{"tid":2235881,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"秋天該很好 你若尚在場","createTime":"2020-10-09T04:54:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T09:24:24.000Z","uid":9394,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"62b09564b57b2926b451915b28cda4921a04d716","tid":2235881,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T04:54:59.000Z","msg":"呢排開始feel到秋天既清風 帶一份凄涼<br />\n諗起十二位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又諗起流亡海外既手足<br />\n又諗起身陷囹圄既手足<br />\n又諗起走左既手足<br />\n又諗起上年呢個時候既香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應承我 不分化不割蓆 多自主思考<br />\n堅持打呢一場唔知打既耐既仗 好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n失去左既人無得翻返黎 但起碼要佢地安息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808df36cc171c9cd7f5ea55f276c5900f9ea2052","tid":2235881,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T07:04:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be51e33c8bc7e4ff153c2f7bc56db00eae8bb895","tid":2235881,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T07:06:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a2c802a10af42829594f45debe811c12f692c8","tid":2235881,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T07:06:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98233a0302fc18b6de5c88b496f2a1bf2c134b8c","tid":2235881,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T07:13:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im